  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose is to build up a data observatory of individuals with thoracic pain evoking acute
      coronary syndrome (ACS). The aim is the characterization of this population of patients
      consulting at emergency department, the evaluation of therapeutic strategies with regard to
      guidelines and the becoming of patients including severe complications and mortality.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
